{"tid":768473,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「看圖作廢文」你俾圖，我寫一段懶感性文","createTime":"2018-08-05T12:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T03:31:24.000Z","uid":196175,"like":6,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"878b9c47334a708e92ba044f908923da68e4a3d8","tid":768473,"uid":196175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/191003_104cb0a742d03dc091b43aa8e596fcec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F191003_104cb0a742d03dc091b43aa8e596fcec.png&h=72fbf6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我和你手牽手在街上漫步<br />\n一滴小水點落在你身上<br />\n這是緣份嗎？<br />\n在萬千個過路人之間選中了你<br />\n你抬頭一看<br />\n笑了笑跟我說<br />\n你像那冷氣機一樣<br />\n我說是因為沒有我不行嗎？<br />\n你笑說是因爲我經常說的笑話都很冷<br />\n我想了想說<br />\n你都很像那冷氣機<br />\n你說為什麼？<br />\n我笑說因為你下面都經常滴水⋯<br />\n<br />\n#求助 #佢打咗我一巴就走 #我講錯啲乜 #感性文 #我平時唔係咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n似呢啲咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1600f2ba27bf38fbe3f376a9e05fcb49fe8e64bb","tid":768473,"uid":138197,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:14:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母好撚柒囉"},{"pid":"6c78dd20a47cfaa338023621bf4dc51d672cd01f","tid":768473,"uid":128223,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"150c8028af93323cd6c0fc6684f11acbfade0bf0","tid":768473,"uid":129660,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:16:31.000Z","msg":"完美演繹&quot;扮撚哂野&quot;"},{"pid":"93701ac9a9c3c2d6e30cebca552a7a66c3e02065","tid":768473,"uid":2419,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/103927_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F103927_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&