like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/231112_f9dc792466e482ab053617fdcabdf6bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F231112_f9dc792466e482ab053617fdcabdf6bd.png&h=33de577a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfa5855735e9914841a397ab35a71d899e66cc0c","tid":768473,"uid":196175,"like":10,"dislike":8,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93701ac9a9c3c2d6e30cebca552a7a66c3e02065","tid":768473,"uid":2419,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/103927_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F103927_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=0f8faef7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"人生有幾多個十年！<br />\n跟隔離屋的老王相識了廿年了<br />\n今天第一次在街坊面前表演很緊張！<br />\n他跟我家人的感情都很好<br />\n還記得以前我在大陸工廠工作<br />\n經常不在家的時候他都會過來幫忙照顧我兒子<br />\n可能是這個緣故吧<br />\n所以人們常說兒子愈大愈像老王他！<br />\n我老婆知道今天我們要表演<br />\n怕單身的老王沒有人關心他<br />\n還特意送了條黃色的新褲子給他漂亮吧<br />\n看見他在表演時<br />\n都不忘指著我身後的老婆跟她單眼表示感謝<br />\n他們關係這麼好我很感恩認識了一個好鄰居！<br />\n<br />\n#感恩 #兄弟 #其他鄰居都很好經常看著我笑 #跳得太落力老王扭親腰了老婆剛過去照顧他 #感性文"},{"pid":"1912f2c48962f4d3ace73bc44015b8317acbe90b","tid":768473,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20150726/s00009/1437895441533SF_D0EC4D6B72D174FCDA04375F8E7B5D56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20150726%2Fs00009%2F1437895441533SF_D0EC4D6B72D174FCDA04375F8E7B5D56.jpg&h=e4ce33d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"799f87ad4d6e61a82c4a9028da935ed55150f396","tid":768473,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfa5855735e9914841a397ab35a71d899e66cc0c","tid":768473,"uid":196175,"like":10,"dislike":8,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93701ac9a9c3c2d6e30cebca552a7a66c3e02065","tid":768473,"uid":2419,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/103927_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F103927_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=0f8faef7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"人生有幾多個十年！<br />\n跟隔離屋的老王相識了廿年了<br />\n今天第一次在街坊面前表演很緊張！<br />\n他跟我家人的感情都很好<br />\n還記得以前我在大陸工廠工作<br />\n經常不在家的時候他都會過來幫忙照顧我兒子<br />\n可能是這個緣故吧<br />\n所以人們常說兒子愈大愈像老王他！<br />\n我老婆知道今天我們要表演<br />\n怕單身的老王沒有人關心他<br />\n還特意送了條黃色的新褲子給他漂亮吧<br />\n看見他在表演時<br />\n都不忘指著我身後的老婆跟她單眼表示感謝<br />\n他們關係這麼好我很感恩認識了一個好鄰居！<br />\n<br />\n#感恩 #兄弟 #其他鄰居都很好經常看著我笑 #跳得太落力老王扭親腰了老婆剛過去照顧他 #感性文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909921e5e49da704612cd723547c288826265663","tid":768473,"uid":68457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93701ac9a9c3c2d6e30cebca552a7a66c3e02065","tid":768473,"uid":2419,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/103927_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F103927_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=0f8faef7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:22:41.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n患癲癇症的鄉民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搖曳的車<br />\n共舞<br />\n於充滿愛的人間"},{"pid":"0b631293a0936fd796a4a7709a274cb1a9ea54c6","tid":768473,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/233314_2a48ec92dfaa0917cb89a2a7c5dacf66.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F233314_2a48ec92dfaa0917cb89a2a7c5dacf66.jpeg&h=c38bc692&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c380d7a56c3107d08929b122c43f919d134d201","tid":768473,"uid":196175,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"49bf3d0c9f392ba68d5a02f65d8a28c09f99f1f4","tid":768473,"uid":5499,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/201813_ddfc504fcc6d79f735af045c9a6d2371.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F201813_ddfc504fcc6d79f735af045c9a6d2371.png&h=37d9bf4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"無敵，是最寂莫<br />\n無敵，最是痛苦<br />\n<br />\n作為太極雙刀門第十八代傳人<br />\n我早已練到落葉都可為刀的境界<br />\n但我修為最高的乃是這紮馬持刀勢<br />\n任你千軍萬馬來進攻<br />\n我都可以絲毫不動<br />\n特意直播這段影片跟大家分享切磋<br />\n歡迎指教<br />\n<br />\n#利申，已經企了廿八個鐘都沒有動過一下 #歡迎閣下廿八個鐘後再來看我作見證 #紮馬 #真功夫"},{"pid":"84b2837be5091801f2460c3102fb66f2082d1c37","tid":768473,"uid":86673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b98d62e260473d414fb21b8dbaf662b4f48965","tid":768473,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/233713_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F233713_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=f8639c15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b73abfeff545a99c060e00944453f30b3f5b0da6","tid":768473,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/233926_345350fd440ffa8340e8f032096d9b18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F233926_345350fd440ffa8340e8f032096d9b18.jpg&h=f63e61bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/233926_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F233926_fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png&h=95cd1317&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e569426aa6b0a7673ed1b94f112467d863daad3f","tid":768473,"uid":196175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19b61e8f1a1eeaea4763f0371d76bb61e0c3e5ce","tid":768473,"uid":143026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/202201_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F202201_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4ff64527&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:42:37.000Z","msg":"你簡單的一言、一笑、一抱，一吻<br />\n竟令我忘掉世界<br />\n<br />\n忘掉妻子，忘掉兒子<br />\n甚至忘掉我自己的身分⋯<br />\n<br />\n謝謝你出現在我的青春裡，謝謝<br />\n<br />\n#想永遠停留在這一刻 #能成為密友大概總帶著愛 #感性文"}]}